title: BRIEF-HUB International Acquires The Assets Der Manouel Insurance & Financial Services

organizations.name: assets der manouel insurance & financial services

text:
February 6, 2018 / 1:05 PM / in 14 minutes BRIEF-HUB International Acquires The Assets Der Manouel Insurance & Financial Services Reuters Staff 
Feb 6 (Reuters) - Hub International Ltd: 
* HUB INTERNATIONAL ACQUIRES THE ASSETS OF CALIFORNIA-BASED DER MANOUEL INSURANCE & FINANCIAL SERVICES, INC. 
* HUB INTERNATIONAL LTD - TERMS OF ACQUISITION WERE NOT DISCLOSED. 
* HUB INTERNATIONAL LTD - ‍DMIG‘S LEADERSHIP TEAM AND STAFF WILL JOIN HUB CALIFORNIA​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
